file.name: one-of-property-level-required.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: unit test
  version: 0.0.1
components:
  schemas:
    employee:
     properties:
       role:
         oneOf: 
         - $ref: "#/components/schemas/doctor"
         - $ref: "#/components/schemas/nurse"
     required:
     - role
      
    nurse:
      properties:
        level:
          type: integer
      required:
      - level
      
    doctor:
      properties:
        income:
          type: number
      required:
      - income
